title: South Korea Tourist Arrivals
description: Tourist Arrivals in South Korea increased to 334351 in September from 308582 in August of 2022. Tourist Arrivals in South Korea averaged 634102.98  from 1993 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1703495  in July of 2016 and a record low of 29415  in April of 2020. This page provides - South Korea Tourist Arrivals - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Korea Tourism Organization
